{"TopicId":153429,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"KIS/KAS has changed EVA","CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-12T22:58:50Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-12T22:58:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi guys!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E installed, and ever since Kerbals on EVA no longer face the way the camera is... which makes navigating hard. Is this normal, and if so any easy way to change it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"IronCretin","CreatedById":158162,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-13T01:41:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry turning on \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E. They only face the camera when \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E is on.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-13T21:55:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}